post.content:
FEEDER STORIES

First of all i want to thanks every one in feeder group of our TCE [24 hour project mates "We wont care about eating ,sleeping,studying,'bathing',itching,door knocking,Even powercut".etc.,during project hours"].........

Feeder~Zasz:-
  Intro             :   T.Chandrasekar,CSE,B.E,TCE
  Role in DOTA :   He is dedicated to his life in every game to get victory,by giving excellent guidance to his parters....
  Conclusion    :   For giving excellent idea's most of the time he wants to be a observer and counting re-spawn time....
  Statements   :   He states that "Kill himself or level up the Roshan or Better be a Observer"

Feeder~Tony:-
  Intro              :   M.Desinghrajan,ECE,B.E,TCE
  Role in DOTA  :   To improve and expanding the DOTA clan ..He is encouraging  beginners by putting team against experienced gamers...
  Conclusion     :   Most of the beginners now improved and some beginners are used as a couriers by him...
  Statements    :   He states that "Die with "0" gold or Splits your gold to Scourge or Sentinel not to Heroes "

Feeder~Samjef :-
  Intro               :   Mano samson,Civil,B.E,Tce
  Role in DOTA   :  To making unknown heroes into favorite heroes in DOTA..No one knows his talent and next step of samson in dota inculing himself...
  Conclusion      :  After 15 loses of continuous combat he had the confident that will get victory in next match..[He knows verywell 16 match also going to loose...Still continuous upto next day also ]...Jesus only helps him....
  Statements     :  He states that "Improve your Aura And stand before tower wait for some time and Feed to enemy not to creeps "

Feeder~Pradeep:-
  Intro                :  M.Pradeep,Mech,B.E,TCE
  Role in dota     :  He wants learn dota like zasz and tony ...still learning...He  want to defeat enemy teammates by considering own mechanical department...Even courier itself wont fear about Feeder~Pradeep...
  Conclusion       :  Most of the time he selects enemy heroes and using their spells...After finding own hero he sent his hero into enemy's moon well by confusing....And fighting with tower until he die "After the lose of victory he remove or delete the game from his PC  ..
  Statements      :  He states that "Do or Die infront of Tower ..Vanthey Matharam"

Feeder~Nitin  :-
  Intro              : Nitin Guntour,ECE,B.E,TCE
  Role in dota   : He wont care about victory or loose of own team....But only aim is to kill the very dangerous neutral creeps..If he dead by neutral creeps [Always 90% dies]he take revenge..He knows the best farming technology .At the end of the game he comes with costly items in his inventory...[because (S)he is the only item in our hostel]...
  Conclusion     : He will surely get the best Kill Stealer And Neutral killer Award in future..He doesnt wear shoe until the match quit..
  Statements    :  He states that "Please Beware of Neutral creeps they are dangerous to DOTA"

Feeder~Muthu  :-
  Intro               : MuthuKrishnan,EEE,B.E,TCE
  Role in DOTA  : He Gang with team players to kill one hero ...after left of his team mates  he still ganging alone with enemy heroes not considering Tower and enemy creeps.. like Vijyakanth... Enemy heroes consider his innocence and leave him into neutral creeps to finish him ...
  Conclusion     : For the frequent use of lightining revenent ICEFROG decides to change  completely and remaked that hero...
  Statements    : He states that "If i gang i will be die If i die i will be a Courier"

Feeder~Maddy   :-
  Intro             : S.Madavan,ECE,B.E,TCE
  Role in dota  :"Atleast getting one victory per day" is ambition of maddy..He accepts any combination of teams with him even beginners..but not with Nitin....he is the excellent player in dota...But not a farmer,kilstealer,ganger,pusher,defender,..Then How?...He foolished by own team mates ..
  Conclusion    : Due to his intelligence and talent his team mates steal his inventory items from circle of power ..nobody even creeps itself allows him to get final kill of heroes,towers..etc..  
  Statements   : he states that "Some one make me victory ..I need one Victory" 

 

 Feeder~Qqqqqq:-
 

  Intro                  : Sivakumar,Mech,B.E,TCE
  Role in dota       : He never choose a hero from tauren .Only by random mode he gets random heroes....But he manages with any unknown heroes(If nitin is there he manages Nitin also as a heroine).....Because of random hero his victory status also random......
  Conclusion         : For more detail contact "Feeder~Nitin"and"Feeder ~Ravi"....Both are calling him as "Matchan","Mama","Dear",etc.
  Statements        : He states that "Nitin is only my property, QQQQq is directly proposal into Nitin,and QQQQQ is Inversly proportional into kamalanathan" 
 
Feeder~Imini       :-

  Intro                      :   Sudhahar,Mech,B.E,TCE
  Role in dota           :  What to do ?He is Beginner  to dota...But somebody begging him to leave from dota ...He never goes alone to combat....HaHaHa...if he goes He wont return to base.....   Some  enemies instead of killing him use as a neutral creap for their time pass..finally he will be used for ganging of their teams..simply like"KIDNAPPING and RAPPING" ..
  Conclusion             :  So noone helps for Imini....I'm very proud of him and i wish him to be a best team leader of our feeder clan..So that We will reach the world of gareana immediately...
  Statements            :  He states that "I am the best player in RPS warcraft3 ..But Noone knows my powers in DoTa...If it continues I will say TaTa to DoTa" 
 
Feeder~6x-xxxxxx       :-
 
  Intro                      :   Balaji Vedarethinam
  Role in dota           :  Mostly after the 1st 3 minutes he shares control of his hero to others so that we may increase his hero level, while he goes afk. When the message shows up that all have been given control of 6x units someone invariably sells his items, thinking he left the game.. thereby getting 0 extra gold and permanantly making him weak.
  Conclusion             :  He has been level 11 for so long that garena administrators put up a special meeting. They decided to upgrade him to level 12 on the basis of sheer boredom.
  Statements            :  He states that "Ayyo endha hero eduthaalum nalla velayaaduranae indha 1_Hp . Goyyala saavu da." 
 

For more updates, Suggestions  and details reply me and coment me.....    "Born to Feed"
